data.description: Check out this house in Franklin just a block from Roland Reynolds Elementary. Sitting on over a half acre lot, this remodeled 3 bedroom 2 bathroom house has a massive backyard with enough space for a playground, pool and or pets. The open concept kitchen and living area sits next to the dining room. Additional storage can be found in the attached carport. Call and schedule your showing today!
